summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1371, for the improvement of Thackeray Place, from East Forty-fifth Street to East Fiftieth Street; East Fiftieth Street, from Thackeray Place to Latona Avenue, and Latona Avenue, from East Fiftieth Street to East Sixty-fifth Street, all in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing the same, under Ordinance No. 15079, and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
